genresAdvancedInfo.name: punjabi lo-fi
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Punjabi lo-fi is a subgenre of lo-fi music that incorporates elements of Punjabi folk music. It is characterized by its relaxed and mellow sound, often featuring acoustic guitar, sitar, and other traditional instruments. The lyrics are often in Punjabi, and the music is known for its soothing and meditative qualities. Punjabi lo-fi is a unique and innovative fusion of traditional and modern music.
